Class SimpleDocumentBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.semanticmetadata.lire.builders.AbstractLocalDocumentBuilder
      • net.semanticmetadata.lire.builders.SimpleDocumentBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DocumentBuilder

    public class SimpleDocumentBuilder
extends AbstractLocalDocumentBuilder
    This class can be used as the LocalDocumentBuilder class, in order to create Lucene Documents according to the SIMPLE model (see features.local.simple package) Created by Nektarios on 03/06/2015.
    Author:
    Nektarios Anagnostopoulos, nek.anag@gmail.com (c) 2015 by Nektarios Anagnostopoulos
